            "title": "梅窩村屋放客廳「尿袋」爆炸焚宅 住戶救火燒傷送院",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"村屋起火冒出白煙。fb梅窩鄉事委員會圖片\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/700fedf5685dc0c10b761389da7f04df/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250515/_2025051515545680960.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">村屋起火冒出白煙。fb梅窩鄉事委員會圖片</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>梅窩鹿地塘村一間村屋於今日（15日）早上11時許發生火警，單位冒出白煙，更一度傳出爆炸聲。44歲姓張男戶主一度嘗試救火但不果，手指燒傷。消防員接報趕到拖喉灌救，最後將火救熄。\n\n</p>\n<p>火警現場是村屋的一樓，警方及消防經初步調查，相信是單位內一個放置在客廳的外置充電器起火，引致火災。事件中張男受傷但清醒，被送往梅窩普通科門診診所治理。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250062/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"消防拖喉救火。fb梅窩鄉事委員會圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4ca779935acf4d7e4504b6d0c2577f32/2025-05/496983336_703760888688756_6615583236114056968_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        消防拖喉救火。fb梅窩鄉事委員會圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250063/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"涉事村屋單位焚毀。fb梅窩鄉事委員會圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/597b889439b61ed6ac0ecbc798840ef1/2025-05/497624457_703760922022086_6678524129621472132_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        涉事村屋單位焚毀。fb梅窩鄉事委員會圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250064/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"fb梅窩鄉事委員會圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/620d752968462f2ddc24cb1a5fff2463/2025-05/497655584_703760832022095_7930012564312531981_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        fb梅窩鄉事委員會圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250065/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"fb梅窩鄉事委員會圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f4ef5c4111409b5e9979b00c30e44f19/2025-05/498175223_703760878688757_8952438836634708094_n.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        fb梅窩鄉事委員會圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250067/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"fb梅窩鄉事委員會圖片\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/523fd4ee8c25ac4f63bbd7d606b4af33/2025-05/1_1_14.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        fb梅窩鄉事委員會圖片\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
